# Codewars Daily Challenge Log  

**Challenge:** [Digital Root](https://www.codewars.com/kata/541c8630095125aba6000c00/solutions/javascript?filter=me&sort=best_practice&invalids=false)  
**Date Completed:** September 2, 2025  
**Difficulty:** 6 kyu  
**Profile:** https://www.codewars.com/users/andysantiagopr  

## Solution (JavaScript)
```js
function digitalRoot(n) {
  let result = n;

  while (result.toString().length > 1) { 
    result = result
      .toString()  // convert the number into a string so it can be split
      .split('')   // break the string into an array of single characters
      .map(Number) // convert each character back into a number
      .reduce((acc, curr) => acc + curr, 0); // sum all digits into a single value
  }

  return result; // return the final single-digit result
}
